            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《机动战士高达 SEED FREEDOM》 剧场版终于也在香港 Netflix 播放了，Bandai 也在近这两个月内也相继推出了《SEED FREEDOM》的两部主角机体模型，HGCE 突击自由高达极，以及 HGCE 无限正义高达二型，这两部高人气机体模型方面表现如何呢？先要说说小编近日比较忙，加上面对著这两部大热人气机体模型，不作一些涂装及上水贴等工序实在不行，今次的评测报告的确是迟来了，请不要见怪啊！既然是迟了，那就连最近的 HGCE 无限正义高达二型制作好了，一起报告吧。</p><p><a title="_DSC0217" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909700865/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909700865_6214accbb9_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0217" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><a title="_DSC0216" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909700895/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909700895_ec6f60d57e_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0216" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>HGCE 无限正义高达二型</h2><p>说实在的，小编是比较喜爱正义高达，多过自由高达，特别是在今次《机动战士高达 SEED FREEDOM》剧场版中的表现，阿斯兰及无限正义高达二式非常亮眼，特别是无限正义高达二式登场时非常惊艳，无限正义在魔蟹外壳中破壳而出，这样的设定已令很多模型高手改装模型，以还原这样的情节。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255320" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9604-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9604-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9604-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>无限正义二式看来与原版差异不大，但仔细比较会发现很多改良之处。关节的银色关节采用了光泽银制作，不是平时一般的银色，看起来更亮眼。胸口取消了绿色轮廓线，整体轮廓更加修长纤细。肩甲尺寸更大。头部保留了长脸尖下巴的特征，但面颊轮廓更直线化。头部侧面火神炮移至头顶，但取消了分色。胸口出气口实现了分色，复合盾牌的黄色部分也采用了分件分色。</p><p><a title="_DSC0227" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909258671/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909258671_e5e78ec285_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0227" width="689" height="1024" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC0241" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909504818/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909504818_d0ca964e8c_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0241" width="1024" height="758" /></a></p><p>骨架方面采用了新型 SEED 系列的设计，整体可动性出色。腰部采用三段式结构，弯腰幅度优秀。肩部可动范围大，手臂前伸和平抬都很到位。膝关节屈膝幅度出色，小腿新增了左右摆动关节，可以摆出更生动的踢姿势。</p><p><a title="_DSC0247" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909603049/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909603049_f609cf70e5_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0247" width="1024" height="697" /></a></p><p>除了原有的光束步枪、复合盾牌等武装外，二式最大的特色是头顶可展开巨大光束军刀。不过模型中这个部件比例偏短小，效果大打折扣，以模型的头部光束军刀长度根本很难会刺中敌机吧？</p><p><a title="_DSC0162" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909564149/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909564149_46396f7830_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0162" width="1024" height="697" /></a></p><p>揹包可变形为支援机，四把光束刀插上后，还原剧中造型，不过外观亦非常似星战的 X-Wing 战机。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255322" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0229-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0229-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc0229.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>Action Pose</h2><p><a title="_DSC0266" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909504813/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909504813_4b62faa278_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0266" width="1024" height="814" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC0232" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909603054/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909603054_ca7f4e654a_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0232" width="1024" height="664" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><a title="_DSC0252" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909258641/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909258641_3b8e18d2b1_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0252" width="1024" height="821" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br />
小编极为期待 Bandai 宣布之后会推出的 HG 1/144 魔蟹 (SEED FREEDOM Ver.)，不知道会是如何设定正义高达塞在魔蟹的体内呢？</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255263" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/452806678_1066628288-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/452806678_1066628288-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/452806678_1066628288.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>模型名称：HGCE 无限正义高达二型<br />
参考售价：2,800 日圆（不含税）<br />
查询：瑞华行</p><h2>HGCE 突击自由高达极</h2><p>突击自由高达极 (之后简称突自极)，与原版突击自由极为相似，部份位置有点改良，整体造型更带点力量感觉，肩部位置采用了新规设计，其中灰色部份肩甲更带来点争议。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255340" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9430-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9430-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9430-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255341" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9438-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9438-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9438-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255342" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9477-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9477-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_9477-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>当然最大亮点就是全新设计的揹包自豪防衞者 PROUD DEFENDER，翅膀采用内外双层叶片结构，展开后可见内部金色叶片，而今次的金色算是比以前一般的模型金色已来得好了，素组派可能会接受到，高点要求的玩家当然就是，自己喷过吧 (小编也是自行喷涂)。虽然有粉红色的 3D 贴纸在缝隙点缀一下，不过亦可能由于是 HG 级模型的关系，小编总感觉这个揹包实在太白净了，制作时唯有尽量加多点水贴，才可以接受到。</p><p><a title="_DSC0200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909504843/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909504843_e94f5a1be5_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0200" width="1024" height="933" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC0201" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909603074/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909603074_d563754309_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0201" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><a title="_DSC0203" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909700880/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909700880_0c1b4c13bd_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0203" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC0120" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53908364537/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53908364537_3196c703fb_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0120" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>另一亮点就是新武器实体武士刀「布都御魂」，在黑色的同一零件上，运用了 2 种表面处理来达到质感差异；分色方面也算是做得不错，唯有在刀柄末端的小小金色部份就需要自己涂装了。</p><p><a title="_DSC0198" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909700890/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909700890_1d8a961ecc_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0198" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>主体部份采用了 SEED 系列最新的关节设计，可动性方面的确是有提升，肩部改为关节组设计，躯干关节有点似飞升自由，腰部和腿部关节也有改良。</p><p><a title="_DSC0168" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53908364517/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53908364517_f39353814a_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0168" width="1024" height="818" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC0175" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909700930/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909700930_eec15fe4d7_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0175" width="1024" height="904" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC0185" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909603099/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909603099_b73f39041a_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0185" width="1024" height="833" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC0191" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909258721/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909258721_a4b92b324f_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0191" width="1024" height="1013" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC0194" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53908364487/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53908364487_79488eeac6_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0194" width="1024" height="998" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC0196" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909700910/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909700910_ce161fb141_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0196" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC0197" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53909504863/in/album-72177720319384842/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53909504863_ac2df976a0_b.jpg" alt="_DSC0197" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>模型名称：HGCE 突击自由高达极<br />
参考售价：2,600 日圆（不含税）<br />
查询：瑞华行</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/08/hgcefreedomjusticeii/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/">【评测】HGCE 突击自由高达极　HGCE 无限正义高达二型</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
