        <item>
            <title>「微信保险」诈骗电话 Cut 线会打来问原因　连登网民分享对付骗徒新招</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/08/wechat-scam/tech-secure/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=wechat-scam</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/08/wechat-scam/tech-secure/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 08:00:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中热话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[资讯保安]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[wechat]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[微信保险]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[诈骗电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[骗案]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1255279</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">最近不少人都有收到「微信保险」的诈骗电话或短讯，声称其开通的微信资金安全保险已经到期，按每月 $2000 收费三年总共需扣费 $72000。网上讨论区同样有网友收到了「微信保险」的诈骗电话，虽未有受骗但抱怨被诈骗电话骚扰，而且骗徒的态度极不友善。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1255294 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2170-1-520x580.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2170-1-520x580.jpg 520w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2170-1.jpg 806w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 520px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3758300/page/2">LIHKG</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">网友抱怨骗徒用几个不同的电话不断向他致电，即使接听后立即挂断电话骗徒也会马上回电，令他十分困扰。他表示骗徒会要求他讲普通话，即使向对方辱骂亦无动于衷。不少网民均表示同样收到了类似的来电和短讯并分享自己的经历，表示「cut 完线即刻再打嚟问我做乜 cut 佢线」、「X 我唔讲普通话」、「上次 X 完佢佢用廿几个唔同号码打嚟」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1255295 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2172-1-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2172-1-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2172-1.jpg 506w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1255296" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2173-1-694x415.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="415" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2173-1-694x415.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2173-1.jpg 1170w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3758300/page/2">LIHKG</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">有网民就分享了不会再被骗徒骚扰的方法，指只需要用纯正的普通话辱骂他们便不会再打来，或向骗徒表示没有安装任何中国大陆的应用程式后，骗徒就会自动挂断电话。有网民以 $2000 太少不在乎来回应骗徒后，更获骗徒祝他身体健康。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1255298 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2176-1-428x580.jpg" alt="" width="428" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2176-1-428x580.jpg 428w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2176-1.jpg 664w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 428px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1255297 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2175-1-694x286.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="286" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2175-1-694x286.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2175-1.jpg 1170w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1255299 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2177-1-e1723099192870-626x580.jpg" alt="" width="626" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2177-1-e1723099192870-626x580.jpg 626w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2177-1-e1723099192870-971x900.jpg 971w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_2177-1-e1723099192870.jpg 1169w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 626px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3758300/page/2">LIHKG</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3758300/page/2">LIHKG</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/26/wellcome-scam/tech-secure/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">SMS 骗案假扮惠康积分换领网站　加 $4.7 换领气炸锅呃信用卡资料</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/03/apple-chinascam/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中国诈骗集团假 iPhone 换真机     Apple 十年被骗超过 9600 万港元</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/03/hkdoublescam/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">警方接获 6 宗网上「二次诈骗」案，苦主被骗后再损失多一次「律师费」</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/08/wechat-scam/tech-secure/">「微信保险」诈骗电话 Cut 线会打来问原因　连登网民分享对付骗徒新招</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
