        <item>
            <title>DJI 无人机帮珠穆朗玛峰清垃圾，运送物资节省人力更安全高效</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/07/nepal-plan-to-use-dji-drones-to-help-clean-up-everest-region-mountain/life-tech/drone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nepal-plan-to-use-dji-drones-to-help-clean-up-everest-region-mountain</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/07/nepal-plan-to-use-dji-drones-to-help-clean-up-everest-region-mountain/life-tech/drone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:00:32 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅游]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[环保]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[航拍]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[dji]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[DJI FlyCart 30]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[无人机]]>
            </category>
