            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">尼泊尔正计划部署 DJI 无人机来取代雪巴人在珠穆朗玛峰地区搬运物资和清理废物，开创高海拔物流领域的先河。这个决定将能大大减低传统上由人类进行搬运的危险任务所带来的风险。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1255144 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/58b0607eb8b24521bcea-694x363.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/58b0607eb8b24521bcea-694x363.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/58b0607eb8b24521bcea.jpeg 1252w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.gizmochina.com/2024/08/07/dji-drones-nepal-moutain-everest/">Gizmochina</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1255146 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/flycartcargo-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/flycartcargo-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/flycartcargo.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://enterprise.dronenerds.com/commercial-drone-platforms/dji-flycart-30/">Drone Nerds Enterprise</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">传统上雪巴人负责在高山运送氧气瓶、帐篷、食物等物资和清理垃圾，每季需要穿越非常危险的冰瀑 30 多次，单单是 1953-2023 年就有近 50 人在冰瀑上丧生。无人机的工作相信会由 DJI 的 FlyCart 30 来执行，最大负重为 30 KG 且支援 6000 米最高飞行海拔高度，能承受 -20°C &#8211; 45°C 的工作环境温度和每秒 12 米的最大抗风速度。前期测试中，DJI 无人机每小时可运送 234 公斤垃圾，同样重量需用上 14 名搬运工和 6 小时才能完成。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_99991"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Hhp11I-vGHA?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">有人指无人机将会夺去了雪巴人的工作，但官员和登山者一致认为无人机将能有效改善安全和环境条件，而无人机的操作亦会交由雪巴人操作。由于人口过度拥挤和气候变化，珠穆朗玛峰地区面临越来越大的挑战，导致废弃物显著累积。无人机预计将在这个脆弱生态系统中发挥关键作用。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://www.gizmochina.com/2024/08/07/dji-drones-nepal-moutain-everest/">Gizmochina</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.gizmochina.com/2024/01/11/dji-flycart-30-long-range-high-payload-design-unveiled/">Gizmochina</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/02/dji-neo-photo-leaked/life-tech/drone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">DJI Neo 小巧航拍机，真机照网上流传</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/31/dji-neo-drone-specs-price-leak/life-tech/drone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">全新航拍机试飞影片外泄，袋装 DJI Neo 零售价格提前曝光</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/02/dji-x-hasselblad/life-tech/drone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">DJI | Hasselblad 哈苏概念店　于澳门新濠影汇正式开业</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/07/nepal-plan-to-use-dji-drones-to-help-clean-up-everest-region-mountain/life-tech/drone/">DJI 无人机帮珠穆朗玛峰清垃圾，运送物资节省人力更安全高效</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
